    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His name yields the richest perfume,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And sweeter than music His voice;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His presence disperses my gloom,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And makes all within me rejoice."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I should, were He always thus nigh,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Have nothing to wish or to fear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No mortal so happy as I;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My summer would last all the year."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Content with beholding His face,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My all to His pleasure resigned;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No changes of season or place,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Would make any change in my mind."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "While blessed with a sense of His love,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A palace a toy would appear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And prisons would palaces prove,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If Jesus would dwell with me there."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My Lord, if indeed I am Thine,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If Thou art my sun and my song,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Say, why do I languish and pine?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And why are my winters so long?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, drive these dark clouds from the sky,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy soul-cheering presence restore;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Or take me to Thee up on high,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where winter and clouds are no more."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    }
